Due to the text-based nature of this requirement, I will create a simple text-based representation of the UI components.

Here is a text-based sketch of the calculator UI:

 Display Area:
  _______________________________________
  |                  (result will display) |
  |_______________________________________|

 Button Row 1:
  +---------------+---------------+
  |                |                |
  |  (7)          |  (8)          |
  |  (4)          |  (9)          |
  |  (1)          |  (0)          |
  +---------------+---------------+

 Button Row 2:
  +---------------+---------------+---------------+
  |                |                |                |
  |  (AC)         |  (+)          |  (Multiply)  |
  |  (Delete)     |  (-)          |  (Divide)     |
  +---------------+---------------+---------------+

 Button Row 3:
  +---------------+---------------+
  |                |                |
  |  (Equals)     |  (Backspace)  |
  |  (Clear)      |  (Period)     |
  +---------------+---------------+


